---
title: Sticky Sweet & Sour Tamarind Chicken with Garlic Rice & Asian Greens
description: A saucy chicken with rice needs an extra large bowl because more is more for this dish. With a sweet and sour tamarind sauce
you’re going to need an A-team of veggies and chicken to match it. A fluffy rice, fragranced with garlic, can help fill up the bowl
and cradle the chicken and veggies.
